{"tid":1891862,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"所有守地抗爭只能以左膠和理非方式進行","createTime":"2020-02-22T06:56:26.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-22T11:46:38.000Z","uid":286685,"like":3,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"ace35c0a71e5d055578421d82a8cdbf25b855bff","tid":1891862,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:56:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/lovenent/photos/a.925576944218926/925577090885578/?type=3&amp;theater\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Flovenent%2Fphotos%2Fa.925576944218926%2F925577090885578%2F%3Ftype%3D3%26theater&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=cbce604a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/lovenent/photos/a.925576944218926/925577090885578/?type=3&amp;theater</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B10Qr9W.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB10Qr9W.jpg&h=ad525e3d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/25941/%E9%A6%AC%E5%B1%8E%E5%9F%94%E6%94%B6%E5%9C%B0-%E7%94%B0%E5%A3%98%E6%95%B5%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8E%E6%8E%A8%E5%9C%9F%E6%A9%9F-%E6%81%92%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%85%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D%E9%8F%9F%E5%8D%A1%E6%9D%BF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F25941%2F%25E9%25A6%25AC%25E5%25B1%258E%25E5%259F%2594%25E6%2594%25B6%25E5%259C%25B0-%25E7%2594%25B0%25E5%25A3%2598%25E6%2595%25B5%25E4%25B8%258D%25E9%2581%258E%25E6%258E%25A8%25E5%259C%259F%25E6%25A9%259F-%25E6%2581%2592%25E5%259C%25B0%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%25B4%25BE%25E5%25B7%25A5%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E6%25B8%2585%25E6%25A9%25AB%25E9%25A1%258D%25E9%258F%259F%25E5%258D%25A1%25E6%259D%25BF&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=1e93219c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/25941/%E9%A6%AC%E5%B1%8E%E5%9F%94%E6%94%B6%E5%9C%B0-%E7%94%B0%E5%A3%98%E6%95%B5%E4%B8%8D%E9%81%8E%E6%8E%A8%E5%9C%9F%E6%A9%9F-%E6%81%92%E5%9C%B0%E4%BB%8A%E6%B4%BE%E5%B7%A5%E4%BA%BA%E6%B8%85%E6%A9%AB%E9%A1%8D%E9%8F%9F%E5%8D%A1%E6%9D%BF</a><br />\n2016年，有班左膠守護馬屎埔村的農地，反對新界東北發展，直到恆基收地。<br />\n果陣我曾經諗過如果那時已有勇武又會如何。<br />\n<br />\n結果理大圍城事件就是答案。<br />\n過千勇武被抄牌<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/402463/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-1-100%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E4%BB%96%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E4%BA%BA\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F402463%2F%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E5%259C%258D%25E5%259F%258E-1-100%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258D%2595%25E6%2588%2596%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E7%2599%25BB%25E8%25A8%2598-%25E4%25BB%2596%25E5%2580%2591%25E6%2598%25AF%25E4%25BB%2580%25E9%25BA%25BC%25E4%25BA%25BA&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=622fca87\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/402463/%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E5%9C%8D%E5%9F%8E-1-100%E4%BA%BA%E8%A2%AB%E6%8D%95%E6%88%96%E8%A2%AB%E7%99%BB%E8%A8%98-%E4%BB%96%E5%80%91%E6%98%AF%E4%BB%80%E9%BA%BC%E4%BA%BA</a><br />\n242勇武為了救守城手足被charge暴動<br />\n<a href=\"https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1641421/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%80%BE200%E4%BA%BA%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E4%BB%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82-%E6%96%99%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E7%9B%B4%E8%87%B3%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1641421%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=59701511\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhd.stheadline.com%2Fnews%2Frealtime%2Fhk%2F1641421%2F%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%2599%2582-%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E-%25E4%25BF%25AE%25E4%25BE%258B%25E9%25A2%25A8%25E6%25B3%25A2-%25E9%2580%25BE200%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%2594%25AF%25E6%258F%25B4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258E%25A7%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595%25E7%25BD%25AA%25E4%25BB%258A%25E6%258F%2590%25E5%25A0%2582-%25E6%2596%2599%25E8%2581%2586%25E8%25A8%258A%25E7%259B%25B4%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%2587%258C%25E6%2599%25A8&h=f983d695\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hd.stheadline.com/news/realtime/hk/1641421/%E5%8D%B3%E6%99%82-%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E-%E4%BF%AE%E4%BE%8B%E9%A2%A8%E6%B3%A2-%E9%80%BE200%E4%BA%BA%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%94%AF%E6%8F%B4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8E%A7%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95%E7%BD%AA%E4%BB%8A%E6%8F%90%E5%A0%82-%E6%96%99%E8%81%86%E8%A8%8A%E7%9B%B4%E8%87%B3%E5%87%8C%E6%99%A8</a><br />\n<br />\n結論是勇武只能用來攻，不能用來守，攻比守更易。<br />\n雖然往後會有新界東北收地，也有守村抗爭，但從理大圍城事件得出的結論是守村抗爭只能以左膠和理非方式進行，否則理大圍城事件將再次於新界東北農地重演，再重演理大圍城勇武就會完全收皮。"},{"pid":"93af69bf4c7c056e42ce52cee81bd29fc5cb00ea","tid":1891862,"uid":70487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T06:59:21.000Z","msg":"和理攻"},{"pid":"ba0483ed22c4f62f801d348bfd1edc396782e14b","tid":1891862,"uid":107681,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T07:01:39.000Z","msg":"反抗軍通常係力量較弱既一方，弱者豈有與強者正面決戰之理<br />\n<br />\n游擊偷襲先係皇道"},{"pid":"6f1b331cb64f8d0af821b09cdabffeb95610e936","tid":1891862,"uid":286685,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-22T11:46:38.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/wangchaugreen/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fwangchaugreen%2F&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=39a65436\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/wangchaugreen/</a><br />\n仲有橫洲收地都係，只能由左膠和理非去守，勇武進場等於送頭。<br />\n因為理大圍城事件已得出勇武不能用來守城。<br />\n勇武手足如要參與守村抗爭要先解除武裝變成左膠和理非，否則理大圍城事件在橫洲再現。<br />\n<br />\n而且鄉郊地方極難be water，鄉郊地方勇武基本上等比人拉暴動坐十碌。<br />\n<br />\n如狗去橫洲收地：<br />\n左膠和理非死守：大批死守橫洲的村民被警方逐一抬走<br />\n勇武火魔守村：離開橫洲的人士，都會被警方以参與暴動罪名拘捕。<br />\n<br />\n政府突收菜園村農地 抬走數名村民<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2011-01-19/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AA%81%E6%94%B6%E8%8F%9C%E5%9C%92%E6%9D%91%E8%BE%B2%E5%9C%B0%20%E6%8A%AC%E8%B5%B0%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91-31621488\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.epochtimes.com%2Fnews%2F2011-01-19%2F%25E6%2594%25BF%25E5%25BA%259C%25E7%25AA%2581%25E6%2594%25B6%25E8%258F%259C%25E5%259C%2592%25E6%259D%2591%25E8%25BE%25B2%25E5%259C%25B0%2520%25E6%258A%25AC%25E8%25B5%25B0%25E6%2595%25B8%25E5%2590%258D%25E6%259D%2591%25E6%25B0%2591-31621488&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=1f8b8f47\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.epochtimes.com/news/2011-01-19/%E6%94%BF%E5%BA%9C%E7%AA%81%E6%94%B6%E8%8F%9C%E5%9C%92%E6%9D%91%E8%BE%B2%E5%9C%B0%20%E6%8A%AC%E8%B5%B0%E6%95%B8%E5%90%8D%E6%9D%91%E6%B0%91-31621488</a><br />\n<br />\n【11.18．理大拆局】警只圍不攻 離開即拘參與暴動 兩類人除外<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/399472/11-18-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%AA%E5%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BB-%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%8B%98%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E5%85%A9%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25AA%2581%25E7%2599%25BC%2F399472%2F11-18-%25E7%2590%2586%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%258B%2586%25E5%25B1%2580-%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E5%258F%25AA%25E5%259C%258D%25E4%25B8%258D%25E6%2594%25BB-%25E9%259B%25A2%25E9%2596%258B%25E5%258D%25B3%25E6%258B%2598%25E5%258F%2583%25E8%2588%2587%25E6%259A%25B4%25E5%258B%2595-%25E5%2585%25A9%25E9%25A1%259E%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E9%2599%25A4%25E5%25A4%2596&d=tV%2Fsyqxl7HZnCfU9ck6AAH%2B3Qbouwy6U%2BTFwRHAqvaY%3D&h=ec509631\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%AA%81%E7%99%BC/399472/11-18-%E7%90%86%E5%A4%A7%E6%8B%86%E5%B1%80-%E8%AD%A6%E5%8F%AA%E5%9C%8D%E4%B8%8D%E6%94%BB-%E9%9B%A2%E9%96%8B%E5%8D%B3%E6%8B%98%E5%8F%83%E8%88%87%E6%9A%B4%E5%8B%95-%E5%85%A9%E9%A1%9E%E4%BA%BA%E9%99%A4%E5%A4%96</a><br />\n<br />\n（一） Be Water(水聚散) 不能變為Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）。<br />\n抗爭運動至今有效，因為Be Water(水聚散)的策略奏效，但從11月11日的「中文大學保衛戰」來看，港青接下來被中共設局引誘，脫離Be Water 路線，陷入Be Castle（碉堡戰、陣地戰）的可能性極大。一旦局面演變為碉堡戰，那就是被「請君入甕」了。"}]}